%% Sequence-Diagramm: Reporting-Aufruf mit Carryover-Lookup.
%% Zeigt Authentication::Full-Bypass für interne Aggregat-Reads.
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Client (Frontend)
    participant REST as REST-Handler<br/>rest/report.rs
    participant Reporting as ReportingService<br/>service_impl/reporting.rs
    participant Perm as PermissionService
    participant Carryover as CarryoverService
    participant SalesPerson as SalesPersonService
    participant Booking as BookingService
    participant ExtraHours as ExtraHoursService
    participant Absence as AbsenceService
    participant CustomEH as CustomExtraHoursService
    participant Toggle as ToggleService

    User->>+REST: GET /report?person=X&from=2026-01-01&to=2026-06-30
    REST->>+Reporting: employee_balance(auth: user, tx=None)
    Reporting->>+Perm: check_role(auth, HR-Viewer)
    Perm-->>-Reporting: Ok

    Note over Reporting: Interne Aggregat-Reads:<br/>Auth wird auf Full hochgehebelt
    Reporting->>+SalesPerson: get(id, Full)
    SalesPerson-->>-Reporting: SalesPerson + Contract-Zeilen
    Reporting->>+Carryover: get_yearly(id, year=2025, Full)
    Note over Carryover,Reporting: Persistierter<br/>Vorjahres-Saldo
    Carryover-->>-Reporting: Carryover(hours, vacation_days)
    Reporting->>+Booking: list_by_person(id, range, Full)
    Booking-->>-Reporting: [Booking...]
    Reporting->>+ExtraHours: list_by_person(id, range, Full)
    ExtraHours->>+CustomEH: get_by_id(uuid, Full)
    CustomEH-->>-ExtraHours: CustomDefinition
    ExtraHours-->>-Reporting: [ExtraHours...]
    Reporting->>+Absence: list_by_person(id, range, Full)
    Absence-->>-Reporting: [Absence-Range...]
    Reporting->>+Toggle: is_enabled("D-51-07", Full)
    Note over Toggle: Full-Bypass<br/>(Phase 51 Gap-Closure)
    Toggle-->>-Reporting: true/false

    Note over Reporting: Berechnung:<br/>Ist = Bookings + ExtraWork<br/>+ Absence-Anteil<br/>Erwartung = Contract × Tage<br/>− SpecialDays − UnpaidLeave<br/>Balance = Ist − Erwartung + Carryover

    Reporting-->>-REST: ReportOutput
    REST-->>-User: 200 OK<br/>ReportTO
